From fc2c90735efa6a8c719c750f4b433777dcf1971d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 18 Jul 2025 17:27:09 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Add compact ppdu end user
 stats structre for qcn9274

ppdu end user stats tlv struct for qcn6432,ipq5332,ipq5442
has 30 DWORDS info and qcn9274 has only 24 DWORDS info.
Adding new compact tlv structure and wmask for qcn9274.

For qcn9274, initialize rx_ppdu_eu_stats_info_get ops pointer
with qcn9274 specific tlv parser API.

Add genmask for all compact TLV structure info.

Patch-dependency:
	0446-0001-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Refactor-HAL-TLV-Parsing-API.patch

Signed-off-by: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
